question: Chiah i-ê ki-lāi-pāng ê hêng-thài ('VR5' ia̍h 'VR6') ū siáⁿ-chi̍t ê tùi 0 kàu 100km/h ê thàu-chhia sî-kan siōng kín?
Tui diesel lia̍k-chhia ngāi-tē, siâng-sî chhut-phìn sî-kan kiat-sû tī 2002 nî í-āu tō kiat-sû ê (kong-lêng CO2 phah-chhut liōng, tan-ūi: g/km) sī siáⁿ-chiàⁿ-ê?
Tshiu-tiāⁿ hō͘ lâng chai ji̍t-chhaⁿ iân-chhut ê tōng-le̍k, i ê CO2 thiah-khì siōng-kē ê sèng-chit?
Tui '1.6 8v' kong-chhia eng-jin ê chè-chok sî-kan, in CO2 phàng-khì hām khek-chhiok tùi 0 kàu 100 km/h ê sî-kan, in chin-chiàⁿ kiàn-kò͘ ū chin-chiàⁿ siáⁿ-siáⁿ piàn-hoà?
answer: Túi hit-khai-sì ê 1999–2000 nî chè-chok liáu-āu, '1.6 8v' kong-chhia eng-jin ū kái-koat. Āu-lâi ê pán-pún, tùi 2000 nî kàu 2006 nî chè-chok, kah sin ê eng-jin ID (AVU/BFQ), CO2 phàng-khì tùi 180 g/km kiám kàu 170 g/km, sī piáu-bī kiat-chè khah iōng-sái. Put-kò, chit ê kái-koat sī ū chió-chió ê lūi-hîng piàn-hó, in 0-100 km/h ê sî-kan tùi 11.9 bián kàu 12.1 bián.

question: Tsik-tsat ē-tōo tsuí-iû hù-lîn kiat-tsap, tsuí-iû sèng-sóo uī 2000 nî tē-gōo uē, koh-iā ē-sái tē 9.5 biáu tsìn tsiū-sì 0 kàu 100 km/h ê miâ-tsū ūi sènn-mih?
Tui-liat ê sîn-chit lóng-chóng ū kúi-ā-ê ū thang sī-tǹg-chò ko-lîm-hêng? Tō sī 0-100km/h khì-sok sī 10.0 kó sek á-sī ke-lāi ê sî, che sī hō͘ lâng-chē-ê siuⁿ-chē sí-luí?
Juah chiah, chi̍t ê sin hō-chháu hē-thóng kā só͘-ū VR5 kap VR6 hùn-chiàⁿ ê CO2 thàu-chhut kiám-chió 15% ê sî, chit-ê te̍k-tēng ê hùn-chiàⁿ cho̍k ê sin siong-tōa CO2 thàu-chhut ē sī kúi-á?

Koa-tē chi̍t-kóa chio̍h-iû (petrol) iâⁿ-chē, chiap-chhiok iâⁿ-chē ê thong-siâⁿ (cc) kah tòe-sok thong-sêng (0-100km/h ê sî-kan) chi-kan ū siáⁿ-mih koan-hē? Chòe-chōe iōng châi-liāu lâi kái-soeh lí ê koan-tiám.
answer: Chio̍h-iû (petrol) iâⁿ-chē ê khoán, iâⁿ-chē ê thong-siâⁿ (cc) kah 0-100km/h ê sî-kan ū chi̍t-ê tōa ê tòe-sok koan-hē. Chit-ê ì-bī sī kóng, chiap-chhiok iâⁿ-chē ê thong-siâⁿ, 0-100km/h ê sî-kan ē chiap-chhiok kiám-chió (thong-sêng ē khah hó). Chē-chē iōng lâi kóng, sió-sió ê chio̍h-iû iâⁿ-chē, 1.4 16v (1390 cc), iōng 15.6 khoo ê sî-kan. Tòe-liáu, siōng-tōa ê iâⁿ-chē, 2.8 24v (2792 cc), iōng 7.6 khoo ê sî-kan. Chit-ê thûi-tōa siòng-tùi chē-chē iâⁿ-chē ê khoán lóng sī kāng-chi̍t ê.

question: Chiah lia̍t ê mi̍h-kiāⁿ tī sia̍p-sûi lāi-bīn sī choân-pō͘ ēng placeholder tsiâⁿ lâi kit-tòng, tì-sú m̄-thang tēⁿ-tòe tsiak-tùi po̍k-choán ê lî-piáⁿ?
Tī lán-ê Diesel lōng-thâu lāi-bīn, ūi-tiāⁿ chi̍t-ê chin tōa-ê chha-bệt, 0 kàu 100 km/h ê sok-tō͘ khah bān, pí kî-thaⁿ só͘ lia̍t-chhut ê Diesel lōng-thâu lóng khah bān, sī-choán ūi-tiāⁿ chi̍t-ê?
Tui ke la̍k-sìⁿ chhia-lāi-kū ū kúi lia̍p sī diesel-chong-sìⁿ?
